OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Henry Leach
OL,5,FHenry Leach, Age 98, Royal Hampshire
OL,6,FRegiment
OL,8,FInterviewed 24 September 2023
OL,10,FSoldiers from the 1st Hampshire
OL,11,FBattalion were among the first British
OL,12,Ftroops ashore on D-Day at T Jig Sector
OL,13,Fof Gold Beach.
OL,15,FHenry Leach landed two weeks later and
OL,16,Fwas a sergeant with the 7th - a
OL,17,Fterritorial battalion from the New
OL,18,FForest.
