OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Henry Leach
OL,5,FHe became involved in heavy fighting
OL,6,Fin Maltot in July, aimed at breaking
OL,7,Fthe German defensive line around Caen.
OL,9,FHe said: "That was a village which we
OL,10,Fhad to take.
OL,12,F"We went down a slope into the village
OL,13,Fand then got to the other side and the
OL,14,FGermans withdrew into a valley and we
OL,15,Fmore or less pinned them down for a
OL,16,Fwhile. Eventually we cleared it up.
