OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Henry Leach
OL,5,F"One unpleasant experience I had, we
OL,6,Fwere preparing to move and I put my
OL,7,Fpack on a little fence and a salvo of
OL,8,Fmortars came, you could hear them,
OL,9,Fnine barrel mortars coming in over the
OL,10,Ftop.
OL,12,F"I dived down into the bottom of the
OL,13,Ftrench. Something came on top of my
OL,14,Fleg and I thought the side of the
OL,15,Ftrench had blown in but it was only my
OL,16,Fpack. It wasn't as frightening as it
OL,17,Fwas at first."
